                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-305-off1656 t18300415-305-cd1657"></join>, 2 lbs. weight of soap, value 14d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-305-victim2552" type="victimName">
